{
  "stem": "8775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ready?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, my father was taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got an order to report for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Hungarian army, in 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was taken from us for several months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But before he left-- and, and the forced labor went with the, with the army itself, and they were working on the Soviet front or Russian front.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before he went, he contacted a friend of his, a medical doctor, and asked for certain pills to be given to him, which would make his heart go-- well, not bad, but which would cause heart troubles to him so, so they would, they would release him, because of a heart condition.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And fortunately, my mom prayed for this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And finally, he showed up at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I think it was no-- without consequence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In other words, he really did damage his heart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He-- when he came back in 1942 until 1944, he was not the same man as we have known him, because of this heart problem, which he pretty much took upon himself by taking these medications, which he probably should not have taken.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the only reason why he took them-- so he can be home and released from, from this forced labor unit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These forced labor units were called [NON-ENGLISH], which is a whole, long name.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But basically, what they were is they were working with the, the armed units.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they had to dig tunnels and bridges and work on airports.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But their equipment was only shovel, so this was-- because they didn't trust the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Otherwise-- and I didn't mention it, that my father was a decorated person from World War I.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He served, I think, two years, in World War I, and-- but this was all disregarded in 1942.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
